Correlation

timecourse_average <- timecourse_data %>%
  group_by(IDD) %>%
  dplyr::summarize(RNA = mean(Copies))

plaque_average <- plaque_assay %>%
  group_by(IDD) %>%
  dplyr::summarise(PFU = mean(Copies))
  
col_data <- merge(timecourse_average, plaque_average, by = "IDD")  

col_data_minus_3 <- col_data %>%
  filter( !str_detect(IDD, "3 hrs"))

correlation <- ggplot(col_data_minus_3,aes(RNA, PFU)) +
  geom_point() +
  scale_y_log10(breaks = trans_breaks("log10", function(x) 10^x),
                labels = trans_format("log10", math_format(10^.x))) +
  scale_x_log10(breaks = trans_breaks("log10", function(x) 10^x),
                labels = trans_format("log10", math_format(10^.x))) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = F) +
  annotate("text", x = 80000, y = 10E5, label = "Spearman R = 0.78, p = 3.665e-07") +
  xlab("ZIKV RNA") +
  ylab("ZIKV PFU/mL")

cor.test(log10(col_data_minus_3$RNA), log10(col_data_minus_3$PFU), method = "spearman")

  filter(Target.Name %in% c("GAPDH","18s rRNA", "GUSB", "HPRT")) %>%
  group_by(Sample.Name) %>%
  dplyr::summarize(HKGeomean = geoMean(averaged_CT))

  filter(Target.Name != "GAPDH",Target.Name != "18s rRNA", Target.Name !="GUSB", Target.Name !="HPRT")
